@startuml
title Outbox publish retry with RabbitMQ

[*] --> PENDING
PENDING --> PROCESSING: scheduler claims due event
FAILED --> PROCESSING: nextAttemptAt reached\nattemptCount < maxAttempts
PROCESSING --> PUBLISHED: RabbitMQ publish succeeds
PROCESSING --> FAILED: RabbitMQ publish fails\nincrement attemptCount
FAILED --> FAILED: max attempts reached\nmanual intervention
PUBLISHED --> [*]

@enduml
